  "detailed_description": "Fight with <strong>blades and wits</strong> in this one hour adaptation of the classic stage play, <i>Cyrano de Bergerac</i>!<br><br>Cyrano is <strong>the greatest swordsman and wordsmith</strong> in all of France. He also has <strong>the largest nose and the fiercest temper</strong>. <br><br>He has stood alone against a hundred soldiers and can best the wits of any poet alive, but when he falls in love with Roxane, he is hopeless. <strong>Could Roxane love a man with a giant nose?</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meanwhile, Roxane has fallen for a beautiful young soldier,</h2>And Cyrano sees an opportunity to share his heart but hide his face.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/4fddc21d0b4e8d84af7396a2bedf9baf.poster.avif?t=1741359561\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/4fddc21d0b4e8d84af7396a2bedf9baf.webm?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/4fddc21d0b4e8d84af7396a2bedf9baf.mp4?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Command your small band of friends in turn based battles!</h2>Journey from Paris to Arras to fight for friendship, honor and love.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e0b0f90282209d2.poster.avif?t=1741359561\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e0b0f90282209d2.webm?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e0b0f90282209d2.mp4?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compose love letters using your own words to win Roxane’s heart!</h2>Collect the full deck of prompt cards to inspire your writing!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/1c50e6ac39062f4239c9b698245e97b0.poster.avif?t=1741359561\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/1c50e6ac39062f4239c9b698245e97b0.webm?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/1c50e6ac39062f4239c9b698245e97b0.mp4?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the poet, the lover, the friend and the fighter.</h2>Take center stage in one of the greatest plays ever written!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/9f3ed838d4a8df3a5498e691e34aeec8.poster.avif?t=1741359561\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/9f3ed838d4a8df3a5498e691e34aeec8.webm?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/9f3ed838d4a8df3a5498e691e34aeec8.mp4?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Fight with <strong>blades and wits</strong> in this one hour adaptation of the classic stage play, <i>Cyrano de Bergerac</i>!<br><br>Cyrano is <strong>the greatest swordsman and wordsmith</strong> in all of France. He also has <strong>the largest nose and the fiercest temper</strong>. <br><br>He has stood alone against a hundred soldiers and can best the wits of any poet alive, but when he falls in love with Roxane, he is hopeless. <strong>Could Roxane love a man with a giant nose?</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meanwhile, Roxane has fallen for a beautiful young soldier,</h2>And Cyrano sees an opportunity to share his heart but hide his face.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/4fddc21d0b4e8d84af7396a2bedf9baf.poster.avif?t=1741359561\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/4fddc21d0b4e8d84af7396a2bedf9baf.webm?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/4fddc21d0b4e8d84af7396a2bedf9baf.mp4?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Command your small band of friends in turn based battles!</h2>Journey from Paris to Arras to fight for friendship, honor and love.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e0b0f90282209d2.poster.avif?t=1741359561\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e0b0f90282209d2.webm?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e